{"tid":830313,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"2016 年砌機List求評+壞左要整想升SPEC","createTime":"2018-09-21T05:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T23:56:17.000Z","uid":119080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d325d1c3ad14c2d50b14c0e305cd5e8e9a14b679","tid":830313,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟係2016年4月行高登出左呢部機<br />\n想問下當年黎講呢部機呢隻SPEC抵唔抵屌 呢個SPEC值唔值5650<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/133833_f7d7f89648af60e433a0f23db94797e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F133833_f7d7f89648af60e433a0f23db94797e5.png&h=201bc307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日部機壞左 拎番去賣呢部機個到整 佢話壞左火牛 同壞左CPU風扇 仲有顯示卡過熱<br />\n<br />\n想問下換咩火牛好同埋換邊隻CPU風扇好<br />\n<br />\n順便想升一升級張顯示卡同RAM<br />\n<br />\n顯卡方面最好可以全力推足推ASUS PG258Q 240HZ MON<br />\n<br />\nRAM就想高頻高mhz小小 請問洗唔洗升夠16GB RAM?<br />\n<br />\n仲有洗唔洗買隻一體式水冷？<br />\n<br />\n主要黎打吃雞PUBG, Warcraft3<br />\n<br />\n希望可以流暢玩到食雞 開槍殺人唔會LAG<br />\n<br />\n之前張GTX 960 2GB 玩吃雞 射人就算描準左都可以打十槍都完全射唔中<br />\n<br />\n仲有想問下warcraft3呢隻game 鎖FPS 66 左右 咁用140HZ/240HZ MON玩比起60HZ玩會唔會有分別？<br />\n<br />\n題外話：其實砌機係咪最好去3C大鋪 例如 Centralfield 正都 Comdex 或者 法奧悠二/T記？"},{"pid":"452232628044db5802a144bbc5bbb0e90f1afa91","tid":830313,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbb9bb2dfefe38bcb9038cbb5e6e8cd7673e0a64","tid":830313,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/133930_29ba5f1d928b5c42403397abf1c55e55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F133930_29ba5f1d928b5c42403397abf1c55e55.png&h=1bf051ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放大d 個SPEC比巴打們睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09